<script>
(function() {
var currentPlayer = 'all';

// ─── POWER DATA (species → stats for card flip) ─────
var powerData = {
'mutant': { name: 'Mutant Gene', stats: [85, 60, 70, 65, 90, 75], desc: 'Born with the X-Gene, this individual possesses innate superhuman abilities that manifested during puberty.' },
'enhanced': { name: 'Super Soldier', stats: [70, 95, 80, 90, 75, 95], desc: 'Enhanced through scientific experimentation, this individual operates at peak human potential and beyond.' },
'inhuman': { name: 'Terrigenesis', stats: [75, 70, 65, 80, 85, 70], desc: 'Transformed by Terrigen Mists, this individual possesses unique abilities tied to their genetic heritage.' },
'human': { name: 'Peak Human', stats: [80, 50, 55, 45, 30, 70], desc: 'No superhuman abilities, but exceptional skill, training, and determination.' },
'alien': { name: 'Extraterrestrial', stats: [80, 85, 90, 85, 80, 80], desc: 'Abilities derived from non-Earth biology and advanced alien physiology.' },
'mystic': { name: 'Arcane Arts', stats: [95, 40, 60, 50, 100, 55], desc: 'Wielder of mystical forces, drawing power from arcane dimensions.' },
'default': { name: 'Unknown', stats: [50, 50, 50, 50, 50, 50], desc: 'Classification pending...' }
};
var statLabels = ['INT', 'STR', 'SPD', 'DUR', 'PWR', 'CMB'];

// ─── CARD RENDERING ─────────────────────────────────
function renderCards(characters) {
var table = document.getElementById('claims-table');
if (!table) return;

// Remove loading placeholder
var loading = table.querySelector('.claims-loading');
if (loading) loading.remove();

characters.forEach(function(c) {
var card = document.createElement('div');
card.className = 'claims-table-item' + (c.group_id ? ' g_' + c.group_id : '');

var imgHtml = c.square_image
? '<div class="faceclaim"><img class="claims-fc-img" src="' + c.square_image + '" alt=""></div>'
: '<div class="faceclaim"></div>';

card.innerHTML = imgHtml
+ '<div class="character">' + (c.name || '') + '</div>'
+ '<div class="codename">' + (c.codename || '') + '</div>'
+ '<div class="fc-name">' + (c.face_claim || '') + '</div>'
+ '<div class="player"><a href="javascript:void(0)">' + (c.alias || '') + '</a></div>'
+ '<div class="joined">' + (c.thread_counts ? c.thread_counts.total + ' threads' : '') + '</div>'
+ '<div class="species" style="display:none">' + (c.species || '').toLowerCase() + '</div>';

card.style.cursor = 'pointer';
card.onclick = function() { window.location.href = c.profile_url; };

table.appendChild(card);
});

updateCount();
populatePlayerList(characters);
populateFcList(characters);
attachFlipHandlers();
}

function updateCount() {
var el = document.getElementById('claims-visible');
if (el) {
el.textContent = document.querySelectorAll('.claims-table-item:not(.claims-hidden)').length;
}
}

// ─── FILTER / SORT ──────────────────────────────────
function filterCards() {
var searchInput = document.getElementById('claims-search-input');
var speciesSelect = document.getElementById('claims-species-select');
var search = searchInput ? searchInput.value.toLowerCase() : '';
var species = speciesSelect ? speciesSelect.value : 'all';

document.querySelectorAll('.claims-table-item').forEach(function(card) {
var text = card.textContent.toLowerCase();
var cardSpecies = (card.querySelector('.species') || {}).textContent || '';
cardSpecies = cardSpecies.toLowerCase();
var cardPlayer = (card.querySelector('.player') || {}).textContent || '';
cardPlayer = cardPlayer.toLowerCase().trim();

var matchSearch = !search || text.indexOf(search) > -1;
var matchSpecies = species === 'all' || cardSpecies.indexOf(species) > -1;
var matchPlayer = currentPlayer === 'all' || cardPlayer === currentPlayer;

if (matchSearch && matchSpecies && matchPlayer) {
card.classList.remove('claims-hidden');
} else {
card.classList.add('claims-hidden');
}
});
updateCount();
}

function sortCards() {
var sortSelect = document.getElementById('claims-sort-select');
var sortBy = sortSelect ? sortSelect.value : 'character';
var table = document.getElementById('claims-table');
if (!table) return;

var cards = Array.from(table.querySelectorAll('.claims-table-item'));
cards.sort(function(a, b) {
var aEl, bEl;
if (sortBy === 'player') { aEl = a.querySelector('.player'); bEl = b.querySelector('.player'); }
else if (sortBy === 'codename') { aEl = a.querySelector('.codename'); bEl = b.querySelector('.codename'); }
else { aEl = a.querySelector('.character'); bEl = b.querySelector('.character'); }

var aVal = (aEl ? aEl.textContent : '').trim().toLowerCase();
var bVal = (bEl ? bEl.textContent : '').trim().toLowerCase();
return aVal.localeCompare(bVal);
});

cards.forEach(function(card) { table.appendChild(card); });
filterCards();
}

// ─── PLAYER MODAL ───────────────────────────────────
function populatePlayerList(characters) {
var list = document.getElementById('claims-player-list');
if (!list) return;
list.innerHTML = '';

var players = {};
characters.forEach(function(c) {
var name = c.alias || '';
if (!name) return;
var key = name.toLowerCase();
if (!players[key]) players[key] = { name: name, count: 0 };
players[key].count++;
});

var sorted = Object.keys(players).sort();
sorted.forEach(function(key) {
var p = players[key];
var div = document.createElement('div');
div.className = 'claims-player-item';
div.setAttribute('data-name', p.name);
div.setAttribute('data-value', key);
div.innerHTML = '<span>' + p.name + '</span><span class="claims-player-item-count">' + p.count + '</span>';
div.onclick = function() { selectPlayer(p.name, key); };
list.appendChild(div);
});
}

function selectPlayer(name, value) {
currentPlayer = value;
var btn = document.getElementById('claims-player-btn');
var btnText = btn ? btn.querySelector('.claims-player-btn-text') : null;
if (btnText) btnText.textContent = name;
if (btn) btn.classList.add('active');
var clearBtn = document.getElementById('claims-player-clear');
if (clearBtn) clearBtn.style.display = 'flex';
closePlayerModal();
filterCards();
}

function clearPlayer() {
currentPlayer = 'all';
var btn = document.getElementById('claims-player-btn');
var btnText = btn ? btn.querySelector('.claims-player-btn-text') : null;
if (btnText) btnText.textContent = 'Player';
if (btn) btn.classList.remove('active');
var clearBtn = document.getElementById('claims-player-clear');
if (clearBtn) clearBtn.style.display = 'none';
filterCards();
}

function openPlayerModal() {
var modal = document.getElementById('claims-player-modal');
if (modal) modal.classList.add('open');
}

function closePlayerModal() {
var modal = document.getElementById('claims-player-modal');
if (modal) modal.classList.remove('open');
var search = document.getElementById('claims-player-modal-search');
if (search) { search.value = ''; filterPlayerList(''); }
}

function filterPlayerList(search) {
search = search.toLowerCase();
document.querySelectorAll('.claims-player-item').forEach(function(item) {
var name = (item.getAttribute('data-name') || '').toLowerCase();
item.style.display = !search || name.indexOf(search) > -1 ? '' : 'none';
});
}

// ─── FACE CLAIMS MODAL ──────────────────────────────
function populateFcList(characters) {
var list = document.getElementById('claims-fc-list');
if (!list) return;
list.innerHTML = '';

var items = [];
characters.forEach(function(c) {
if (c.face_claim) items.push({ fc: c.face_claim, char: c.name || '' });
});
items.sort(function(a, b) { return a.fc.localeCompare(b.fc); });

items.forEach(function(item) {
var div = document.createElement('div');
div.className = 'claims-fc-item';
div.setAttribute('data-fc', item.fc.toLowerCase());
div.innerHTML = '<span class="claims-fc-name">' + item.fc + '</span><span class="claims-fc-char">' + item.char + '</span>';
list.appendChild(div);
});
}

function filterFcList(search) {
search = search.toLowerCase();
document.querySelectorAll('.claims-fc-item').forEach(function(item) {
var fc = (item.getAttribute('data-fc') || '');
item.style.display = !search || fc.indexOf(search) > -1 ? '' : 'none';
});
}

// ─── CARD FLIP ANIMATION ────────────────────────────
var flipOverlay, flipCard, flipCloseBtn, currentSourceCard;

function createFlipElements() {
if (flipOverlay) return;

flipOverlay = document.createElement('div');
flipOverlay.style.cssText = 'position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;background:rgba(0,0,0,0);z-index:100000;pointer-events:none;transition:background 0.4s ease;';
flipOverlay.onclick = closeFlipModal;

flipCloseBtn = document.createElement('button');
flipCloseBtn.style.cssText = 'position:fixed;top:20px;right:20px;z-index:100002;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);background:rgba(0,0,0,0.5);color:#fff;cursor:pointer;font-size:24px;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;';
flipCloseBtn.innerHTML = '<i class="material-icons">close</i>';
flipCloseBtn.onclick = closeFlipModal;

flipCard = document.createElement('div');
flipCard.style.cssText = 'position:fixed;z-index:100001;transform-style:preserve-3d;display:none;';
flipCard.innerHTML = '<div id="flip-card-front" style="position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;backface-visibility:hidden;overflow:hidden;border-radius:12px;"></div>'
+ '<div id="flip-card-back" style="position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;backface-visibility:hidden;transform:rotateY(180deg);overflow:hidden;border-radius:12px;background:#1a1a2e;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;"></div>';

document.body.appendChild(flipOverlay);
document.body.appendChild(flipCloseBtn);
document.body.appendChild(flipCard);
}

function openFlipModal(card) {
createFlipElements();
currentSourceCard = card;
var rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
var front = flipCard.querySelector('#flip-card-front');
var back = flipCard.querySelector('#flip-card-back');

// Clone card into front
front.innerHTML = '';
front.appendChild(card.cloneNode(true));

// Build back with power data
var speciesEl = card.querySelector('.species');
var speciesKey = speciesEl ? speciesEl.textContent.trim().toLowerCase() : 'default';
var data = powerData[speciesKey] || powerData['default'];

var barsHtml = '';
for (var i = 0; i < 6; i++) {
barsHtml += '<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin:4px 0;">'
+ '<span style="width:32px;font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);opacity:0.7;">' + statLabels[i] + '</span>'
+ '<div style="flex:1;height:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;">'
+ '<div style="width:' + data.stats[i] + '%;height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ff6b9d,#9d4edd);border-radius:4px;transition:width 0.6s ease ' + (i * 0.1) + 's;"></div>'
+ '</div>'
+ '<span style="font-size:11px;font-family:var(--mono);opacity:0.5;">' + data.stats[i] + '</span>'
+ '</div>';
}

back.innerHTML = '<div style="padding:20px;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ff6b9d,#9d4edd);"><div style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:4px;opacity:0.8;">POWER PROFILE</div></div>'
+ '<div style="padding:20px;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">'
+ '<div style="font-size:14px;font-family:var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;">' + data.name + '</div>'
+ barsHtml
+ '<div style="font-size:12px;opacity:0.6;margin-top:auto;">' + data.desc + '</div>'
+ '</div>'
+ '<div style="padding:10px;text-align:center;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:2px;opacity:0.4;">CLICK TO CLOSE</div>';

// Set initial position
flipCard.style.left = rect.left + 'px';
flipCard.style.top = rect.top + 'px';
flipCard.style.width = rect.width + 'px';
flipCard.style.height = rect.height + 'px';
flipCard.style.transform = 'rotateY(0deg)';
flipCard.style.transition = 'none';
flipCard.style.display = 'block';
card.style.visibility = 'hidden';

flipOverlay.style.pointerEvents = 'auto';
flipCloseBtn.style.display = 'flex';

// Animate to center
requestAnimationFrame(function() {
requestAnimationFrame(function() {
flipCard.style.transition = 'all 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)';
flipCard.style.left = (window.innerWidth / 2 - 160) + 'px';
flipCard.style.top = (window.innerHeight / 2 - 240) + 'px';
flipCard.style.width = '320px';
flipCard.style.height = '480px';
flipCard.style.transform = 'rotateY(180deg)';
flipOverlay.style.background = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.92)';
});
});
}

function closeFlipModal() {
if (!currentSourceCard) return;
var rect = currentSourceCard.getBoundingClientRect();

flipCloseBtn.style.display = 'none';
flipOverlay.style.background = 'rgba(0,0,0,0)';
flipOverlay.style.pointerEvents = 'none';

flipCard.style.transition = 'all 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)';
flipCard.style.left = rect.left + 'px';
flipCard.style.top = rect.top + 'px';
flipCard.style.width = rect.width + 'px';
flipCard.style.height = rect.height + 'px';
flipCard.style.transform = 'rotateY(0deg)';

setTimeout(function() {
currentSourceCard.style.visibility = '';
flipCard.style.display = 'none';
currentSourceCard = null;
}, 650);
}

function attachFlipHandlers() {
document.querySelectorAll('.claims-table-item').forEach(function(card) {
if (card.getAttribute('data-flip-attached')) return;
card.setAttribute('data-flip-attached', 'true');
card.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
e.stopPropagation();
openFlipModal(card);
});
});
}

// ─── EVENT BINDINGS ─────────────────────────────────
function bindEvents() {
var searchInput = document.getElementById('claims-search-input');
var sortSelect = document.getElementById('claims-sort-select');
var speciesSelect = document.getElementById('claims-species-select');
var playerBtn = document.getElementById('claims-player-btn');
var playerClear = document.getElementById('claims-player-clear');
var playerModalClose = document.getElementById('claims-modal-close');
var playerModalSearch = document.getElementById('claims-player-modal-search');
var playerModal = document.getElementById('claims-player-modal');
var fcBtn = document.getElementById('claims-fc-btn');
var fcModalSearch = document.getElementById('claims-fc-modal-search');
var fcModal = document.getElementById('claims-fc-modal');
var fcModalClose = document.getElementById('claims-fc-modal-close');

if (searchInput) searchInput.addEventListener('input', filterCards);
if (sortSelect) sortSelect.addEventListener('change', sortCards);
if (speciesSelect) speciesSelect.addEventListener('change', filterCards);
if (playerBtn) playerBtn.addEventListener('click', openPlayerModal);
if (playerClear) playerClear.addEventListener('click', clearPlayer);
if (playerModalClose) playerModalClose.addEventListener('click', closePlayerModal);
if (playerModalSearch) playerModalSearch.addEventListener('input', function() { filterPlayerList(this.value); });
if (playerModal) playerModal.addEventListener('click', function(e) { if (e.target === playerModal) closePlayerModal(); });
if (fcBtn) fcBtn.addEventListener('click', function() { var m = document.getElementById('claims-fc-modal'); if (m) m.classList.add('open'); });
if (fcModalClose) fcModalClose.addEventListener('click', function() { var m = document.getElementById('claims-fc-modal'); if (m) m.classList.remove('open'); });
if (fcModalSearch) fcModalSearch.addEventListener('input', function() { filterFcList(this.value); });
if (fcModal) fcModal.addEventListener('click', function(e) { if (e.target === fcModal) { fcModal.classList.remove('open'); } });
}

// ─── INIT ───────────────────────────────────────────
function initClaims() {
var table = document.getElementById('claims-table');
if (!table) return false;

bindEvents();

WatcherAPI.getClaims().then(function(characters) {
if (!characters || !characters.length) {
table.innerHTML = '<div class="ptt-empty">No characters found</div>';
return;
}
// Batch-fetch square_image for card thumbnails
var ids = characters.map(function(c) { return c.id; });
WatcherAPI.getFields(ids, ['square_image']).then(function(fields) {
characters.forEach(function(c) {
var f = fields[c.id] || {};
c.square_image = f.square_image || '';
});
renderCards(characters);
}).catch(function() {
renderCards(characters);
});
}).catch(function(err) {
console.log('[Claims] API error:', err);
table.innerHTML = '<div class="ptt-empty">Failed to load claims</div>';
});

return true;
}

if (!initClaims()) {
var checkInterval = setInterval(function() {
if (initClaims()) clearInterval(checkInterval);
}, 200);
setTimeout(function() { clearInterval(checkInterval); }, 10000);
}
})();
</script>
<!-- Profile Audio Player -->
<script>
(function() {
var API_BASE = "https://audio.imagehut.ch";

function initProfileAudioPlayer() {
var card = document.querySelector('.profile-audio-card');
if (!card) return false;

var playlistUrl = card.getAttribute('data-playlist-url');
if (!playlistUrl || playlistUrl.trim() === '') {
card.style.display = 'none';
return true;
}

var player = card.querySelector('.profile-audio-player');
if (!player) return false;

var statusEl = player.querySelector('.pap-status');
var nowEl = player.querySelector('.pap-now');
var titleEl = player.querySelector('.pap-title');
var visualizerWrap = player.querySelector('.pap-visualizer-wrap');
var visualizerCanvas = player.querySelector('.pap-visualizer');
var controlsEl = player.querySelector('.pap-controls');
var prevBtn = player.querySelector('.pap-prev');
var playBtn = player.querySelector('.pap-play');
var nextBtn = player.querySelector('.pap-next');
var progressWrap = player.querySelector('.pap-progress-wrap');
var progressBar = player.querySelector('.pap-progress-bar');
var progressEl = player.querySelector('.pap-progress');
var timeEl = player.querySelector('.pap-time');
var listWrap = player.querySelector('.pap-list-wrap');
var listEl = player.querySelector('.pap-list');
var audio = player.querySelector('.pap-audio');
var refreshBtn = card.querySelector('.pap-refresh');
var debugBtn = card.querySelector('.pap-debug-btn');
var debugPanel = player.querySelector('.pap-debug');
var logEl = player.querySelector('.pap-log');
var headerTitle = card.querySelector('.pap-header-title');
var playingTitle = card.querySelector('.pap-title-playing');

var tracks = [];
var currentIndex = 0;
var playlistData = null;
var debugVisible = false;
var audioCtx = null;
var analyser = null;
var dataArray = null;
var animationId = null;

function log(msg) {
if (!logEl) return;
var ts = new Date().toISOString().substr(11, 8);
logEl.textContent += '[' + ts + '] ' + msg + '\n';
logEl.scrollTop = logEl.scrollHeight;
console.log('[AudioPlayer] ' + msg);
}

function formatTime(s) {
if (isNaN(s)) return '0:00';
var m = Math.floor(s / 60);
var sec = Math.floor(s % 60);
return m + ':' + (sec < 10 ? '0' : '') + sec;
}

function setStatus(msg, isError) {
statusEl.textContent = msg;
statusEl.className = isError ? 'pap-status error' : 'pap-status';
log('STATUS: ' + msg + (isError ? ' [ERROR]' : ''));
}

function showPlayer() {
statusEl.style.display = 'none';
nowEl.style.display = 'block';
visualizerWrap.style.display = 'flex';
controlsEl.style.display = 'flex';
listWrap.style.display = 'block';
initVisualizer();
}

function initVisualizer() {
if (audioCtx || !visualizerCanvas) return;
try {
audioCtx = new (window.AudioContext || window.webkitAudioContext)();
analyser = audioCtx.createAnalyser();
analyser.fftSize = 256;
var source = audioCtx.createMediaElementSource(audio);
source.connect(analyser);
analyser.connect(audioCtx.destination);
dataArray = new Uint8Array(analyser.frequencyBinCount);
log('Visualizer initialized');
} catch (e) {
log('Visualizer error: ' + e.message);
}
}

var particles = [];
var hueShift = 0;
var energyHistory = [];
var lastBeatTime = 0;

function drawVisualizer() {
if (!analyser || !visualizerCanvas) return;
var ctx = visualizerCanvas.getContext('2d');
var width = visualizerWrap.offsetWidth;
var height = visualizerWrap.offsetHeight;
visualizerCanvas.width = width;
visualizerCanvas.height = height;

analyser.getByteFrequencyData(dataArray);
ctx.clearRect(0, 0, width, height);

// Beat detection - focus on bass frequencies (first ~10% of spectrum)
var bassEnd = Math.floor(dataArray.length * 0.1);
var bassEnergy = 0;
for (var b = 0; b < bassEnd; b++) {
bassEnergy += dataArray[b];
}
bassEnergy /= bassEnd;

// Track energy history (last ~30 frames)
energyHistory.push(bassEnergy);
if (energyHistory.length > 30) energyHistory.shift();

// Calculate average and detect beat
var avgEnergy = energyHistory.reduce(function(a, b) { return a + b; }, 0) / energyHistory.length;
var now = Date.now();
var isBeat = bassEnergy > avgEnergy * 1.3 && bassEnergy > 100 && (now - lastBeatTime) > 100;
if (isBeat) lastBeatTime = now;

var halfBars = 48;
var barWidth = width / (halfBars * 2);
var gap = 1;
var step = Math.floor(dataArray.length / halfBars);
var centerX = width / 2;
var centerY = height / 2;

var style = getComputedStyle(card);
var gbg1 = style.getPropertyValue('--gbg1').trim() || '255,100,150';
var gbg2 = style.getPropertyValue('--gbg2').trim() || gbg1;
var r1 = gbg1.split(',').map(parseFloat);
var r2 = gbg2.split(',').map(parseFloat);

// Slowly shift hue for color animation
hueShift = (hueShift + 0.3) % 360;

// Progress fill - simple rectangle with top/bottom feather
var progress = audio.duration ? (audio.currentTime / audio.duration) : 0;
if (progress > 0) {
var progWidth = width * progress;

// Vertical gradient - transparent at top/bottom, visible in middle
var vertGrad = ctx.createLinearGradient(0, 0, 0, height);
vertGrad.addColorStop(0, 'rgba(' + gbg1 + ', 0)');
vertGrad.addColorStop(0.25, 'rgba(' + gbg1 + ', 0.12)');
vertGrad.addColorStop(0.5, 'rgba(' + gbg2 + ', 0.15)');
vertGrad.addColorStop(0.75, 'rgba(' + gbg1 + ', 0.12)');
vertGrad.addColorStop(1, 'rgba(' + gbg1 + ', 0)');

ctx.fillStyle = vertGrad;
ctx.fillRect(0, 0, progWidth, height);
}

// Draw mirrored bars with glow
for (var i = 0; i < halfBars; i++) {
var value = dataArray[i * step];
var barHeight = (value / 255) * height * 0.8;
var y = centerY - barHeight / 2;
var alpha = 0.5 + (value / 255) * 0.4;

// Gradient from center (gbg1) to edges (gbg2) with subtle hue shift
var t = i / halfBars;
var hueOffset = Math.sin((hueShift + i * 3) * Math.PI / 180) * 15;
var r = Math.min(255, Math.max(0, Math.round(r1[0] * (1-t) + r2[0] * t + hueOffset)));
var g = Math.min(255, Math.max(0, Math.round(r1[1] * (1-t) + r2[1] * t)));
var b = Math.min(255, Math.max(0, Math.round(r1[2] * (1-t) + r2[2] * t - hueOffset)));
var color = r + ',' + g + ',' + b;

// Glow effect
ctx.shadowBlur = 6 + (value / 255) * 12;
ctx.shadowColor = 'rgba(' + gbg1 + ', 0.4)';
ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(' + color + ', ' + alpha + ')';

// Right side
var xRight = centerX + (i * barWidth);
ctx.fillRect(xRight + gap, y, barWidth - gap * 2, barHeight);

// Left side (mirror)
var xLeft = centerX - ((i + 1) * barWidth);
ctx.fillRect(xLeft + gap, y, barWidth - gap * 2, barHeight);

// Spawn particles - beat-reactive with more on beats
var isEdge = i > halfBars * 0.5;
var baseChance = isEdge ? 0.7 : 0.88;
var spawnChance = isBeat ? baseChance * 0.3 : baseChance; // 3x more likely on beat
var sizeBoost = isBeat ? 1.5 : 1;
var speedBoost = isBeat ? 1.8 : 1;
if (value > 80 && Math.random() > spawnChance) {
// Top particle
particles.push({
x: xRight + barWidth/2 + (Math.random()-0.5) * 6,
y: y - 5,
vx: (Math.random() - 0.5) * 1.2 * speedBoost,
vy: (-Math.random() * 0.8 - 0.3) * speedBoost,
life: 1,
size: (Math.random() * 2.5 + 1) * sizeBoost,
color: color
});
particles.push({
x: xLeft + barWidth/2 + (Math.random()-0.5) * 6,
y: y - 5,
vx: (Math.random() - 0.5) * 1.2 * speedBoost,
vy: (-Math.random() * 0.8 - 0.3) * speedBoost,
life: 1,
size: (Math.random() * 2.5 + 1) * sizeBoost,
color: color
});
// Bottom particle
particles.push({
x: xRight + barWidth/2 + (Math.random()-0.5) * 6,
y: y + barHeight + 5,
vx: (Math.random() - 0.5) * 1.2 * speedBoost,
vy: (Math.random() * 0.8 + 0.3) * speedBoost,
life: 1,
size: (Math.random() * 2.5 + 1) * sizeBoost,
color: color
});
particles.push({
x: xLeft + barWidth/2 + (Math.random()-0.5) * 6,
y: y + barHeight + 5,
vx: (Math.random() - 0.5) * 1.2 * speedBoost,
vy: (Math.random() * 0.8 + 0.3) * speedBoost,
life: 1,
size: (Math.random() * 2.5 + 1) * sizeBoost,
color: color
});
}
}

// Draw and update particles
ctx.shadowBlur = 0;
for (var p = particles.length - 1; p >= 0; p--) {
var part = particles[p];
part.x += part.vx;
part.y += part.vy;
part.life -= 0.008; // Very slow fade

// Remove if dead or too many
if (part.life <= 0 || particles.length > 150) {
particles.splice(p, 1);
continue;
}

// Fade particles near edges of canvas
var edgeFade = 1;
if (part.y < 10) edgeFade = part.y / 10;
if (part.y > height - 10) edgeFade = (height - part.y) / 10;

var pulse = 0.7 + Math.sin(Date.now() * 0.008 + p) * 0.3;
ctx.shadowBlur = 12 * part.life;
ctx.shadowColor = 'rgba(' + part.color + ', ' + (part.life * pulse * edgeFade) + ')';
ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(' + part.color + ', ' + (part.life * edgeFade) + ')';
ctx.beginPath();
ctx.arc(part.x, part.y, part.size * part.life * 1.2, 0, Math.PI * 2);
ctx.fill();
}

animationId = requestAnimationFrame(drawVisualizer);
}

function startVisualizer() {
if (audioCtx && audioCtx.state === 'suspended') audioCtx.resume();
if (!animationId) drawVisualizer();
}

function stopVisualizer() {
if (animationId) {
cancelAnimationFrame(animationId);
animationId = null;
}
particles = [];
if (visualizerCanvas) {
var ctx = visualizerCanvas.getContext('2d');
ctx.clearRect(0, 0, visualizerCanvas.width, visualizerCanvas.height);
}
}

function renderList() {
listEl.innerHTML = '';
for (var i = 0; i < tracks.length; i++) {
var t = tracks[i];
var li = document.createElement('li');
li.textContent = (i + 1) + '. ' + t.title;
li.setAttribute('data-index', i);
if (t.status === 'pending' || t.status === 'processing') {
li.className = 'pending';
} else if (t.status === 'error') {
li.className = 'error';
} else if (i === currentIndex) {
li.className = 'active';
}
(function(idx, track) {
li.addEventListener('click', function() {
if (track.status === 'complete') playTrack(idx);
});
})(i, t);
listEl.appendChild(li);
}
}

function playTrack(idx) {
if (idx < 0 || idx >= tracks.length) return;
var t = tracks[idx];
if (t.status !== 'complete') return;
currentIndex = idx;
var trackApiUrl = API_BASE + '/api/track/' + t.id;
log('PLAY: ' + t.title);

// Fetch direct R2 URL for CORS compatibility with visualizer
fetch(trackApiUrl)
.then(function(r) { return r.json(); })
.then(function(data) {
log('R2 URL: ' + data.url);
audio.src = data.url;
audio.play();
})
.catch(function(e) {
log('Track fetch error: ' + e.message);
});

titleEl.textContent = t.title;
if (playingTitle) playingTitle.textContent = t.title;
if (headerTitle) headerTitle.classList.add('playing');
playBtn.innerHTML = '<i class="material-icons">pause</i>';
renderList();
}

function updateButtons() {
var hasReady = false;
for (var i = 0; i < tracks.length; i++) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { hasReady = true; break; } }
playBtn.disabled = !hasReady;
var hasPrev = false;
for (var i = currentIndex - 1; i >= 0; i--) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { hasPrev = true; break; } }
prevBtn.disabled = !hasPrev;
var hasNext = false;
for (var i = currentIndex + 1; i < tracks.length; i++) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { hasNext = true; break; } }
nextBtn.disabled = !hasNext;
}

function loadPlaylist(forceRefresh) {
setStatus(forceRefresh ? 'Refreshing playlist...' : 'Loading playlist...');
var url = API_BASE + '/api/playlist' + (forceRefresh ? '?refresh=true' : '');
log('POST ' + url);
log('Body: ' + JSON.stringify({ url: playlistUrl }));
fetch(url, {
method: 'POST',
headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
body: JSON.stringify({ url: playlistUrl })
})
.then(function(r) {
log('Response: ' + r.status + ' ' + r.statusText);
if (!r.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + r.status);
return r.json();
})
.then(function(data) {
log('Tracks: ' + data.tracks.length + ', Status: ' + data.status);
playlistData = data;
tracks = data.tracks;
if (tracks.length === 0) { setStatus('No tracks found', true); return; }
var hasReady = false;
for (var i = 0; i < tracks.length; i++) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { hasReady = true; break; } }
if (hasReady) {
showPlayer();
renderList();
updateButtons();
} else if (data.status === 'pending' || data.status === 'processing') {
setStatus('Processing tracks...');
pollUpdates();
} else if (data.status === 'error') {
setStatus('Failed to process', true);
}
})
.catch(function(e) {
log('FETCH ERROR: ' + e.message);
setStatus('Error: ' + e.message, true);
})
.finally(function() {
if (refreshBtn) {
refreshBtn.disabled = false;
refreshBtn.classList.remove('refreshing');
}
});
}

function pollUpdates() {
if (!playlistData) return;
var url = API_BASE + '/api/playlist/' + playlistData.id;
log('GET ' + url);
fetch(url)
.then(function(r) {
log('Poll response: ' + r.status);
return r.json();
})
.then(function(data) {
playlistData = data;
tracks = data.tracks;
var hasReady = false, allDone = true;
for (var i = 0; i < tracks.length; i++) {
if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') hasReady = true;
if (tracks[i].status !== 'complete' && tracks[i].status !== 'error') allDone = false;
}
log('Poll: hasReady=' + hasReady + ', allDone=' + allDone);
if (hasReady) { showPlayer(); renderList(); updateButtons(); }
if (!allDone) { setTimeout(pollUpdates, 3000); } else { renderList(); }
})
.catch(function(e) {
log('Poll error: ' + e.message);
setTimeout(pollUpdates, 5000);
});
}

audio.addEventListener('error', function() {
log('AUDIO ERROR: ' + (audio.error ? audio.error.message : 'unknown'));
});

playBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
if (audio.paused) {
if (audio.src) { audio.play(); }
else {
for (var i = 0; i < tracks.length; i++) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { playTrack(i); break; } }
}
} else { audio.pause(); }
});

prevBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
for (var i = currentIndex - 1; i >= 0; i--) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { playTrack(i); break; } }
});

nextBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
for (var i = currentIndex + 1; i < tracks.length; i++) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { playTrack(i); break; } }
});

if (refreshBtn) {
refreshBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
if (refreshBtn.disabled) return;
refreshBtn.disabled = true;
refreshBtn.classList.add('refreshing');
audio.pause();
audio.src = '';
loadPlaylist(true);
});
}

if (debugBtn && debugPanel) {
debugBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
debugVisible = !debugVisible;
debugPanel.style.display = debugVisible ? 'block' : 'none';
debugBtn.classList.toggle('active', debugVisible);
});
}

audio.addEventListener('play', function() {
playBtn.innerHTML = '<i class="material-icons">pause</i>';
if (headerTitle) headerTitle.classList.add('playing');
startVisualizer();
});
audio.addEventListener('pause', function() {
playBtn.innerHTML = '<i class="material-icons">play_arrow</i>';
if (headerTitle) headerTitle.classList.remove('playing');
stopVisualizer();
});
audio.addEventListener('ended', function() {
for (var i = currentIndex + 1; i < tracks.length; i++) { if (tracks[i].status === 'complete') { playTrack(i); return; } }
playBtn.innerHTML = '<i class="material-icons">play_arrow</i>';
if (headerTitle) headerTitle.classList.remove('playing');
stopVisualizer();
});
audio.addEventListener('timeupdate', function() {
if (audio.duration) {
if (progressEl) progressEl.style.width = (audio.currentTime / audio.duration * 100) + '%';
timeEl.textContent = formatTime(audio.currentTime) + ' / ' + formatTime(audio.duration);
}
});
// Click on canvas bottom area to seek
// Click anywhere on visualizer to seek
visualizerCanvas.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
if (!audio.duration) return;
var rect = visualizerCanvas.getBoundingClientRect();
var clickX = e.clientX - rect.left;
var progress = Math.max(0, Math.min(1, clickX / rect.width));
audio.currentTime = progress * audio.duration;
});
visualizerCanvas.style.cursor = 'pointer';

log('Player init');
log('API_BASE: ' + API_BASE);
log('PLAYLIST_URL: ' + playlistUrl);
loadPlaylist();
return true;
}

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
if (!initProfileAudioPlayer()) {
var checkInterval = setInterval(function() {
if (initProfileAudioPlayer()) clearInterval(checkInterval);
}, 200);
setTimeout(function() { clearInterval(checkInterval); }, 5000);
}
});
})();
</script>

<!-- Mini Profile Audio Bar (Post Row Slide-Out Player) -->
<script>
(function() {
var API_BASE = "https://audio.imagehut.ch";

function initMiniProfileAudio() {
// Find all play buttons in post rows
var playButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.pr-play-btn');
if (playButtons.length === 0) return false;

playButtons.forEach(function(btn) {
if (btn.hasAttribute('data-audio-init')) return;
btn.setAttribute('data-audio-init', 'true');

btn.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
e.stopPropagation();

var sidebar = btn.closest('.pr-sidebar');
if (!sidebar) return;

var playlistUrl = sidebar.getAttribute('data-playlist-url');
if (!playlistUrl || playlistUrl.trim() === '') return;

var postWrap = sidebar.closest('.pr-wrap');
if (!postWrap) return;

var audioBar = postWrap.querySelector('.pr-audio-bar');
if (!audioBar) return;

// Initialize and show the audio bar
initAudioBar(audioBar, playlistUrl, sidebar);
});
});

return true;
}

function initAudioBar(bar, playlistUrl, sidebar) {
var inner = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-bar-inner');
var canvas = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-visualizer');
var controls = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-controls');
var prevBtn = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-prev');
var playBtn = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-play');
var nextBtn = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-next');
var titleEl = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-title');
var timeEl = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-time');
var closeBtn = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-close');
var audio = bar.querySelector('.pr-audio-element');

if (!audio || !playBtn) return;

// State
var tracks = [];
var currentIndex = 0;
var isPlaying = false;
var audioCtx = null;
var analyser = null;
var dataArray = null;
var animationId = null;

// Get colors from sidebar (post author's group colors)
var style = getComputedStyle(sidebar);
var gbg1 = style.getPropertyValue('--gbg1').trim() || '33, 138, 244';
var gbg2 = style.getPropertyValue('--gbg2').trim() || '241, 212, 50';

function formatTime(s) {
if (isNaN(s)) return '0:00';
var m = Math.floor(s / 60);
var sec = Math.floor(s % 60);
return m + ':' + (sec < 10 ? '0' : '') + sec;
}

function updateTime() {
if (timeEl && audio) {
timeEl.textContent = formatTime(audio.currentTime) + ' / ' + formatTime(audio.duration);
}
}

function updatePlayIcon() {
var icon = playBtn.querySelector('i');
if (icon) {
icon.textContent = isPlaying ? 'pause' : 'play_arrow';
}
}

function loadTrack(index) {
if (index < 0 || index >= tracks.length) return;
currentIndex = index;
var track = tracks[index];

if (track.status === 'ready' && track.url) {
audio.src = track.url;
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = track.title || 'Track ' + (index + 1);
audio.load();
}
}

function play() {
if (audioCtx && audioCtx.state === 'suspended') {
audioCtx.resume();
}
audio.play().then(function() {
isPlaying = true;
updatePlayIcon();
startVisualizer();
}).catch(function(e) {
console.log('[MiniAudio] Play failed:', e);
});
}

function pause() {
audio.pause();
isPlaying = false;
updatePlayIcon();
stopVisualizer();
}

function togglePlay() {
if (isPlaying) {
pause();
} else {
play();
}
}

function nextTrack() {
var next = (currentIndex + 1) % tracks.length;
loadTrack(next);
if (isPlaying) play();
}

function prevTrack() {
var prev = (currentIndex - 1 + tracks.length) % tracks.length;
loadTrack(prev);
if (isPlaying) play();
}

function shuffleArray(arr) {
for (var i = arr.length - 1; i > 0; i--) {
var j = Math.floor(Math.random() * (i + 1));
var temp = arr[i];
arr[i] = arr[j];
arr[j] = temp;
}
return arr;
}

function initVisualizer() {
if (audioCtx || !canvas) return;
try {
audioCtx = new (window.AudioContext || window.webkitAudioContext)();
analyser = audioCtx.createAnalyser();
analyser.fftSize = 64;
var source = audioCtx.createMediaElementSource(audio);
source.connect(analyser);
analyser.connect(audioCtx.destination);
dataArray = new Uint8Array(analyser.frequencyBinCount);
} catch (e) {
console.log('[MiniAudio] Visualizer init failed:', e);
}
}

function startVisualizer() {
if (!canvas || !analyser || !dataArray) return;
var ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');

function draw() {
animationId = requestAnimationFrame(draw);
analyser.getByteFrequencyData(dataArray);

canvas.width = canvas.offsetWidth;
canvas.height = canvas.offsetHeight;
ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);

var barCount = dataArray.length;
var barWidth = canvas.width / barCount;

for (var i = 0; i < barCount; i++) {
var barHeight = (dataArray[i] / 255) * canvas.height;
var x = i * barWidth;
var y = canvas.height - barHeight;

// Gradient from gbg1 to gbg2
var ratio = i / barCount;
ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(' + gbg1 + ', ' + (0.4 + ratio * 0.3) + ')';
ctx.fillRect(x, y, barWidth - 1, barHeight);
}
}
draw();
}

function stopVisualizer() {
if (animationId) {
cancelAnimationFrame(animationId);
animationId = null;
}
}

function closeAudioBar() {
pause();
bar.classList.remove('active');
audio.src = '';
tracks = [];
currentIndex = 0;
}

// Event listeners
playBtn.addEventListener('click', togglePlay);
if (prevBtn) prevBtn.addEventListener('click', prevTrack);
if (nextBtn) nextBtn.addEventListener('click', nextTrack);
if (closeBtn) closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closeAudioBar);

audio.addEventListener('timeupdate', updateTime);
audio.addEventListener('ended', function() {
// Shuffle: play random next track
var randomIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * tracks.length);
loadTrack(randomIndex);
play();
});
audio.addEventListener('canplay', function() {
updateTime();
});

// Show the bar
bar.classList.add('active');
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = 'Loading...';

// Fetch playlist
fetch(API_BASE + '/api/playlist', {
method: 'POST',
headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
body: JSON.stringify({ url: playlistUrl })
})
.then(function(r) { return r.json(); })
.then(function(data) {
if (data.error) {
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = 'Error: ' + data.error;
return;
}

// Poll for tracks
var playlistId = data.playlist_id;
pollTracks(playlistId);
})
.catch(function(e) {
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = 'Failed to load';
console.log('[MiniAudio] Fetch error:', e);
});

function pollTracks(playlistId) {
fetch(API_BASE + '/api/playlist/' + playlistId)
.then(function(r) { return r.json(); })
.then(function(data) {
if (data.error) {
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = 'Error';
return;
}

tracks = data.tracks || [];
var readyTracks = tracks.filter(function(t) { return t.status === 'ready'; });

if (readyTracks.length === 0) {
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = 'Processing...';
setTimeout(function() { pollTracks(playlistId); }, 2000);
return;
}

// Shuffle and start playing
tracks = shuffleArray(readyTracks);
initVisualizer();
loadTrack(0);
play();
})
.catch(function(e) {
if (titleEl) titleEl.textContent = 'Error';
console.log('[MiniAudio] Poll error:', e);
});
}
}

// Initialize on DOM ready and after dynamic content loads
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
initMiniProfileAudio();
});

// Re-init when new posts are loaded (for pagination)
var observer = new MutationObserver(function(mutations) {
mutations.forEach(function(m) {
if (m.addedNodes.length > 0) {
initMiniProfileAudio();
}
});
});

var target = document.getElementById('innerwrapper');
if (target) {
observer.observe(target, { childList: true, subtree: true });
}
})();
</script>

<!-- Mobile Nav Scroll-Away (forum-wide) -->
<script>
(function() {
// Only run on mobile
if (window.innerWidth > 1024) return;

var headerNav = document.querySelector('.header-nav');
if (!headerNav) return;

var lastScrollY = 0;
var scrollUpAmount = 0;
var scrollUpThreshold = 40; // Pixels of upward scroll to trigger show
var hideThreshold = 80; // Don't hide until scrolled this far down
var ticking = false;

function updateNavState() {
var currentScrollY = window.scrollY;
var scrollDelta = currentScrollY - lastScrollY;

if (currentScrollY < hideThreshold) {
// Near top - always show
headerNav.classList.remove('nav-scrolled');
scrollUpAmount = 0;
} else if (scrollDelta < 0) {
// Scrolling up - accumulate and check threshold
scrollUpAmount += Math.abs(scrollDelta);
if (scrollUpAmount > scrollUpThreshold) {
headerNav.classList.remove('nav-scrolled');
}
} else if (scrollDelta > 0) {
// Scrolling down - hide and reset counter
headerNav.classList.add('nav-scrolled');
scrollUpAmount = 0;
}

lastScrollY = currentScrollY;
ticking = false;
}

window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
if (!ticking) {
requestAnimationFrame(updateNavState);
ticking = true;
}
}, { passive: true });
})();
</script>

<!-- Profile Thread Tracker (API-powered via WatcherAPI) -->
<script>
(function() {
var initialized = false;

function initProfileThreadTracker() {
var container = document.querySelector('.profile-thread-tracker');
if (!container || initialized) return !container ? false : true;
initialized = true;

var userId = container.dataset.userId;
var loadingEl = container.querySelector('.ptt-loading');
var contentEl = container.querySelector('.ptt-content');

// Fallback: get user ID from URL if data attribute is empty or unparsed
if (!userId || userId === '' || userId.indexOf('|id|') !== -1) {
var urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
userId = urlParams.get('showuser');
}
if (!userId) {
if (loadingEl) loadingEl.textContent = 'No user ID available.';
return true;
}

// Fetch threads and all quotes in parallel from The Watcher API
var threadsPromise = WatcherAPI.getCharacterThreads(userId);
var quotesPromise = WatcherAPI.getCharacterQuotes(userId);

threadsPromise.then(function(data) {
renderTracker(data, contentEl, loadingEl);
}).catch(function() {
if (loadingEl) loadingEl.textContent = 'Failed to load threads.';
});

quotesPromise.then(function(quotes) {
if (!quotes || !quotes.length) return;
var quoteContainer = document.querySelector('.profile-ooc-quote');
var quoteEl = document.querySelector('.ptt-random-quote');
if (!quoteContainer || !quoteEl) return;

var currentIndex = Math.floor(Math.random() * quotes.length);
quoteEl.textContent = quotes[currentIndex].quote_text;
quoteContainer.classList.add('has-quote');

// Add cycling button if more than one quote
if (quotes.length > 1) {
var cycleBtn = document.createElement('button');
cycleBtn.className = 'ptt-quote-cycle';
cycleBtn.title = 'Another quote';
cycleBtn.innerHTML = '<i class="material-symbols-outlined">refresh</i>';
cycleBtn.addEventListener('click', function() {
var nextIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % quotes.length;
currentIndex = nextIndex;
quoteEl.style.opacity = '0';
setTimeout(function() {
quoteEl.textContent = quotes[currentIndex].quote_text;
quoteEl.style.opacity = '1';
}, 200);
});
quoteContainer.appendChild(cycleBtn);
}
}).catch(function() { /* quotes are non-critical */ });

return true;
}

function renderTracker(data, contentEl, loadingEl) {
var categories = ['ongoing', 'comms', 'complete', 'incomplete'];
var icons = { ongoing: 'edit', comms: 'forum', complete: 'check_circle', incomplete: 'hourglass_empty' };
var labels = { ongoing: 'Ongoing', comms: 'Comms', complete: 'Complete', incomplete: 'Incomplete' };
var counts = data.counts || {};
var total = (counts.ongoing || 0) + (counts.comms || 0) + (counts.complete || 0) + (counts.incomplete || 0);

if (total === 0) {
if (contentEl) contentEl.innerHTML = '<div class="ptt-empty">No threads found</div>';
if (loadingEl) loadingEl.style.display = 'none';
return;
}

// Determine first non-empty tab
var firstTab = '';
for (var i = 0; i < categories.length; i++) {
if (data[categories[i]] && data[categories[i]].length > 0) { firstTab = categories[i]; break; }
}

var html = '';

html += '<div class="ptt-subtabs">';
categories.forEach(function(cat) {
html += '<input type="radio" id="ptt-tab-' + cat + '" name="ptt-tabs"' + (cat === firstTab ? ' checked' : '') + '>';
});

html += '<div class="ptt-bar">';
html += '<div class="ptt-slider"></div>';
categories.forEach(function(cat) {
var count = counts[cat] || 0;
if (count === 0) return;
html += '<label for="ptt-tab-' + cat + '" class="ptt-bar-item">';
html += '<i class="material-symbols-outlined">' + icons[cat] + '</i>';
html += '<strong>' + count + '</strong>';
html += '<span>' + labels[cat] + '</span>';
html += '</label>';
});
html += '</div>';

categories.forEach(function(cat) {
html += '<div class="ptt-panel" id="ptt-panel-' + cat + '"><ul class="ptt-thread-list" id="ptt-list-' + cat + '"></ul></div>';
});
html += '</div>';

if (contentEl) contentEl.innerHTML = html;
if (loadingEl) loadingEl.style.display = 'none';

// Populate lists
categories.forEach(function(cat) {
var threads = data[cat] || [];
var listEl = document.getElementById('ptt-list-' + cat);
var showStatus = cat !== 'complete';
var showCompletedBadge = cat === 'complete';
renderThreadList(threads, showStatus, showCompletedBadge, listEl);
});

// Sliding indicator
var bar = contentEl.querySelector('.ptt-bar');
var slider = bar && bar.querySelector('.ptt-slider');
if (bar && slider) {
function moveSlider(animate) {
var subtabs = bar.closest('.ptt-subtabs');
var checked = subtabs && subtabs.querySelector('input[name="ptt-tabs"]:checked');
if (!checked) return;
var label = bar.querySelector('label[for="' + checked.id + '"]');
if (!label) return;
var barRect = bar.getBoundingClientRect();
var labelRect = label.getBoundingClientRect();
if (!animate) slider.style.transition = 'none';
slider.style.left = (labelRect.left - barRect.left) + 'px';
slider.style.width = labelRect.width + 'px';
if (!animate) { slider.offsetHeight; slider.style.transition = ''; }
}
moveSlider(false);
var radios = bar.closest('.ptt-subtabs').querySelectorAll('input[name="ptt-tabs"]');
for (var r = 0; r < radios.length; r++) {
radios[r].addEventListener('change', function() { moveSlider(true); });
}
}
}

function timeAgo(isoStr) {
if (!isoStr) return null;
var d = new Date(isoStr);
if (isNaN(d)) return null;
var secs = Math.floor((Date.now() - d) / 1000);
if (secs < 60) return 'just now';
var mins = Math.floor(secs / 60);
if (mins < 60) return mins + 'm ago';
var hrs = Math.floor(mins / 60);
if (hrs < 24) return hrs + 'h ago';
var days = Math.floor(hrs / 24);
if (days < 30) return days + 'd ago';
var months = Math.floor(days / 30);
if (months < 12) return months + 'mo ago';
return Math.floor(months / 12) + 'y ago';
}

function renderThreadList(threads, showStatus, showCompletedBadge, listEl) {
if (!listEl) return;
threads.forEach(function(t) {
var isUserLastPoster = t.is_user_last_poster;
var li = document.createElement('li');
li.className = (isUserLastPoster ? 'ptt-replied' : 'ptt-awaiting') + (showCompletedBadge ? ' ptt-completed' : '');
li.setAttribute('data-thread-id', t.id);

var html = '';
if (showStatus) {
var icon = isUserLastPoster ? 'check' : 'close';
var title = isUserLastPoster ? 'Waiting on partner' : 'Your turn to reply';
html += '<span class="ptt-status" title="' + title + '"><i class="material-symbols-outlined">' + icon + '</i></span>';
}
if (showCompletedBadge) {
html += '<span class="ptt-completed-badge" title="Completed"><i class="material-symbols-outlined">star</i></span>';
}
html += '<div class="ptt-thread-info">';
html += '<div class="ptt-thread-title"><a href="' + t.url + '">' + t.title + '</a></div>';

// Meta line: partner name + forum link
var meta = [];
if (t.last_poster_name) {
var partnerLink = t.last_poster_id
? '<a href="index.php?showuser=' + t.last_poster_id + '" class="ptt-partner-link">' + t.last_poster_name + '</a>'
: t.last_poster_name;
meta.push('Last Poster: ' + partnerLink);
}
if (t.forum_name) {
var forumLink = t.forum_id
? '<a href="index.php?showforum=' + t.forum_id + '">' + t.forum_name + '</a>'
: t.forum_name;
meta.push(forumLink);
}
if (meta.length) {
html += '<div class="ptt-thread-meta">' + meta.join(' <span class="ptt-meta-sep">·</span> ') + '</div>';
}
var ago = timeAgo(t.last_post_date);
if (ago) {
html += '<div class="ptt-date">' + ago + '</div>';
}

html += '</div>';

// Excerpt floats in the negative space - always from the last poster
if (t.last_post_excerpt) {
var safe = t.last_post_excerpt.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;').replace(/"/g,'&quot;');
html += '<div class="ptt-thread-excerpt">' + safe + '</div>';
}

html += '<div class="ptt-avatar" title="Last post by ' + (t.last_poster_name || '') + '">';
if (t.last_poster_avatar) {
html += '<img src="' + t.last_poster_avatar + '" alt="">';
} else {
html += '<i class="material-symbols-outlined ptt-avatar-fallback">person</i>';
}
html += '</div>';

li.innerHTML = html;
listEl.appendChild(li);
});
}

if (!initProfileThreadTracker()) {
var check = setInterval(function() {
if (initProfileThreadTracker()) clearInterval(check);
}, 200);
setTimeout(function() { clearInterval(check); }, 5000);
}
});
})();
</script>

// Early console capture for debug panel (log + warn)
(function() {
window.__earlyLogs = [];
function capture(level, orig, args) {
orig.apply(console, args);
var msg = Array.from(args).map(function(a) {
return typeof a === 'object' ? JSON.stringify(a) : String(a);
}).join(' ');
window.__earlyLogs.push({ msg: msg, level: level });
}
var origLog = console.log;
var origWarn = console.warn;
console.log = function() { capture('log', origLog, arguments); };
console.warn = function() { capture('warn', origWarn, arguments); };
})();

// Power Grid stat bar conversion (API-powered via WatcherAPI)
(function() {
var animatedUsers = {};

var gridObserver = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries) {
entries.forEach(function(entry) {
if (entry.isIntersecting) {
var container = entry.target;
var sidebar = container.closest('.pr-sidebar');
var userId = sidebar ? sidebar.getAttribute('data-user-id') : null;

if (userId && animatedUsers[userId]) {
setFillsInstant(container);
} else {
animateFills(container);
if (userId) animatedUsers[userId] = true;
}
gridObserver.unobserve(container);
}
});
}, { threshold: 0.2 });

function setFillsInstant(container) {
container.querySelectorAll('.profile-stat-fill, .pr-stat-fill').forEach(function(fill) {
var pct = fill.getAttribute('data-pct');
if (pct) {
fill.style.width = pct;
var bar = fill.closest('.profile-stat-bar, .pr-stat-bar');
if (bar) bar.style.setProperty('--pct', parseFloat(pct));
}
});
}

function animateFills(container) {
container.querySelectorAll('.profile-stat-fill, .pr-stat-fill').forEach(function(fill, index) {
var pct = fill.getAttribute('data-pct');
if (pct) {
setTimeout(function() {
fill.style.width = pct;
var bar = fill.closest('.profile-stat-bar, .pr-stat-bar');
if (bar) bar.style.setProperty('--pct', parseFloat(pct));
}, 100 + (index * 80));
}
});
}

function processFills(fills, container) {
var needsObserver = false;
fills.forEach(function(fill, index) {
var rawValue = fill.getAttribute('data-value') || '';
var match = rawValue.match(/(\d+)/);
var value = match ? parseInt(match[1], 10) : null;
var bar = fill.closest('.profile-stat-bar, .pr-stat-bar');
if (bar.querySelector('.stat-value')) return;

var valueSpan = document.createElement('span');
valueSpan.className = 'stat-value';

if (value !== null && value >= 1 && value <= 7) {
valueSpan.textContent = value;
bar.insertBefore(valueSpan, fill);
var pct = ((value / 7) * 100);
fill.setAttribute('data-pct', pct + '%');
needsObserver = true;
} else if (value !== null && (value === 0 || value > 7)) {
valueSpan.textContent = value;
bar.insertBefore(valueSpan, fill);
fill.style.background = '#ff3333';
fill.closest('.profile-stat, .pr-stat').classList.add('invalid-stat');
fill.style.width = '100%';
}
});
if (needsObserver && container) gridObserver.observe(container);
}

function fetchPowerGridFromAPI(userId) {
return WatcherAPI.getFields([userId], ['power grid - int', 'power grid - str', 'power grid - spd', 'power grid - dur', 'power grid - pwr', 'power grid - cmb'])
.then(function(data) {
var fields = data[userId] || {};
return [
fields['power grid - int'] || '',
fields['power grid - str'] || '',
fields['power grid - spd'] || '',
fields['power grid - dur'] || '',
fields['power grid - pwr'] || '',
fields['power grid - cmb'] || ''
];
});
}

function setupPowerGrid() {
var containers = document.querySelectorAll('.profile-stats, .pr-stats, .pr-power-grid');
if (!containers.length) return false;

containers.forEach(function(container) {
if (container.dataset.powerGridInit) return;
container.dataset.powerGridInit = 'true';

var fills = container.querySelectorAll('.profile-stat-fill, .pr-stat-fill');
var hasEmptyValues = Array.from(fills).every(function(fill) {
return !(fill.getAttribute('data-value') || '').trim();
});

if (hasEmptyValues) {
var sidebar = container.closest('.pr-sidebar');
var userId = sidebar ? sidebar.getAttribute('data-user-id') : null;
if (!userId) {
var tracker = document.querySelector('.profile-thread-tracker[data-user-id]');
userId = tracker ? tracker.getAttribute('data-user-id') : null;
}
if (!userId) {
var m = window.location.search.match(/showuser=(\d+)/);
userId = m ? m[1] : null;
}
if (userId) {
(function(cont) {
fetchPowerGridFromAPI(userId).then(function(values) {
if (values && values.length) {
var contFills = cont.querySelectorAll('.profile-stat-fill, .pr-stat-fill');
contFills.forEach(function(fill, i) {
if (values[i]) fill.setAttribute('data-value', values[i]);
});
processFills(contFills, cont);
}
}).catch(function() {});
})(container);
}
} else {
processFills(fills, container);
}
});
return true;
}

setupPowerGrid();
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() { setupPowerGrid(); });
window.disabledEventListener('disabled', function() { setupPowerGrid(); });
var target = document.getElementById('innerwrapper') || document.body;
var observer = new MutationObserver(function() { setupPowerGrid(); });
observer.observe(target, { childList: true, subtree: true });
})(); </script>

<script>
(function() {
// === Scroll to Top ===
var scrollBtn = document.getElementById('scroll-top-btn');
if (scrollBtn) {
scrollBtn.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
});
}

// === Text Size ===
var KEY = 'twaitheme_text_size';
var MIN = 1, MAX = 5, DEFAULT = 3;
var downBtn = document.getElementById('text-size-down');
var upBtn = document.getElementById('text-size-up');

function getLevel() {
var n = parseInt(localStorage.getItem(KEY), 10);
return (n >= MIN && n <= MAX) ? n : DEFAULT;
}

function applyLevel(level) {
if (level === DEFAULT) {
document.body.removeAttribute('data-text-size');
} else {
document.body.setAttribute('data-text-size', level);
}
downBtn.classList.toggle('at-limit', level <= MIN);
upBtn.classList.toggle('at-limit', level >= MAX);
}

function setLevel(level) {
level = Math.max(MIN, Math.min(MAX, level));
localStorage.setItem(KEY, level);
applyLevel(level);
}

applyLevel(getLevel());

downBtn.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
var level = getLevel();
if (level > MIN) setLevel(level - 1);
});
upBtn.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
e.preventDefault();
var level = getLevel();
if (level < MAX) setLevel(level + 1);
});
})();
</script>

<script>
(function() {
var panel = document.getElementById('debug-panel');
var content = document.getElementById('debug-content');
var stats = document.getElementById('debug-stats');
var fab = document.getElementById('debug-btn');
var filters = document.querySelectorAll('.debug-filter');
var currentFilter = 'all';
var counts = { api: 0, claims: 0, audio: 0, staff: 0, star: 0, blur: 0, other: 0 };

function getCategory(msg) {
if (msg.indexOf('[Staff]') !== -1) return 'staff';
if (msg.indexOf('[AudioPlayer]') !== -1 || msg.indexOf('[MiniAudio]') !== -1) return 'audio';
if (msg.indexOf('[Claims]') !== -1) return 'claims';
if (msg.indexOf('[CharPanel]') !== -1) return 'api';
if (msg.indexOf('[Blur]') !== -1) return 'blur';
if (msg.indexOf('Star-tab') !== -1) return 'star';
if (msg.indexOf('WatcherAPI') !== -1) return 'api';
return 'other';
}

function updateStats() {
var parts = [];
Object.keys(counts).forEach(function(k) {
if (counts[k] > 0) parts.push('<span>' + k + ': ' + counts[k] + '</span>');
});
stats.innerHTML = parts.join('');
}

function applyFilter() {
content.querySelectorAll('.log-line').forEach(function(line) {
if (currentFilter === 'all') {
line.classList.remove('hidden');
} else {
line.classList.toggle('hidden', !line.classList.contains(currentFilter));
}
});
}

// Helper to add a log line to the panel
function addLogLine(msg, level) {
var cat = getCategory(msg);
counts[cat] = (counts[cat] || 0) + 1;
var line = document.createElement('div');
line.className = 'log-line ' + cat;
if (level === 'warn') line.classList.add('warn');
if (currentFilter !== 'all' && cat !== currentFilter) line.classList.add('hidden');
line.textContent = msg;
content.appendChild(line);
}

// Replay early logs captured before debug panel existed
if (window.__earlyLogs && window.__earlyLogs.length) {
window.__earlyLogs.forEach(function(entry) {
if (typeof entry === 'string') { addLogLine(entry, 'log'); }
else { addLogLine(entry.msg, entry.level); }
});
content.scrollTop = content.scrollHeight;
updateStats();
}

// Intercept console.log + console.warn going forward
function makeInterceptor(level, orig) {
return function() {
orig.apply(console, arguments);
var msg = Array.from(arguments).map(function(a) {
return typeof a === 'object' ? JSON.stringify(a) : String(a);
}).join(' ');
addLogLine(msg, level);
content.scrollTop = content.scrollHeight;
updateStats();
};
}
console.log = makeInterceptor('log', console.log);
console.warn = makeInterceptor('warn', console.warn);

// Filter buttons
filters.forEach(function(btn) {
btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
filters.forEach(function(b) { b.classList.remove('active'); });
btn.classList.add('active');
currentFilter = btn.dataset.filter;
applyFilter();
});
});

// Toggle/close/clear
fab.addEventListener('click', function(e) { e.preventDefault(); panel.classList.toggle('open'); });
document.getElementById('debug-close').addEventListener('click', function() { panel.classList.remove('open'); });
document.getElementById('debug-clear').addEventListener('click', function() {
content.innerHTML = '';
counts = { api: 0, claims: 0, audio: 0, staff: 0, star: 0, blur: 0, other: 0 };
updateStats();
});

updateStats();
})();
</script>

<!-- Completed thread counter for mini profiles (API-powered via WatcherAPI) -->
<script>
(function() {
function applyThreadCounts() {
var sidebars = document.querySelectorAll('.pr-sidebar[data-user-id]');
if (!sidebars.length) return;

// Collect unique user IDs
var seen = {};
sidebars.forEach(function(s) {
var uid = s.getAttribute('data-user-id');
if (uid && !seen[uid]) seen[uid] = true;
});

// Fetch thread counts for each unique user
Object.keys(seen).forEach(function(uid) {
WatcherAPI.getThreadCounts(uid).then(function(counts) {
if (!counts || !counts.complete) return;
// Apply to all sidebars for this user
document.querySelectorAll('.pr-sidebar[data-user-id="' + uid + '"]').forEach(function(s) {
var countEl = s.querySelector('.pr-complete-count');
var labelEl = s.querySelector('.pr-complete-label');
var boxEl = s.querySelector('.pr-complete');
if (!countEl) return;
if (counts.complete > 0) {
countEl.textContent = counts.complete;
if (labelEl) labelEl.textContent = 'complete';
if (boxEl) boxEl.classList.add('has-count');
}
});
}).catch(function() { /* non-critical */ });
});
}

document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', applyThreadCounts);
})();
</script>

<!-- Webhook: Ping The Watcher on form submissions -->
<script>
document.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
var form = e.target;
if (!form.action) return;

// New post / reply
if (form.action.indexOf('act=Post') !== -1) {
var threadMatch = form.action.match(/t=(\d+)/);
var forumMatch = form.action.match(/f=(\d+)/);
WatcherAPI.sendActivity('new_post', {
thread_id: threadMatch ? threadMatch[1] : null,
forum_id: forumMatch ? forumMatch[1] : null
});
}

// New topic
if (form.action.indexOf('act=Post') !== -1 && form.action.indexOf('CODE=02') !== -1) {
var forumMatch2 = form.action.match(/f=(\d+)/);
WatcherAPI.sendActivity('new_topic', {
forum_id: forumMatch2 ? forumMatch2[1] : null
});
}

// Profile edit
if (form.action.indexOf('act=UserCP') !== -1 && form.action.indexOf('CODE=04') !== -1) {
WatcherAPI.sendActivity('profile_edit', {
user_id: (document.body.className.match(/group-\d+/) || [''])[0]
});
}
});
</script>

<!-- Backdrop-filter fix - must run AFTER debug panel to capture logs -->
<script>
(function() {
const elementsNeedingBlur = ['.header-nav'];

elementsNeedingBlur.forEach(selector => {
const el = document.querySelector(selector);
if (!el) {
console.log('[Blur] Element not found:', selector);
return;
}

// Check the element itself first
const elComputed = getComputedStyle(el);
console.log('[Blur] === Checking:', selector, '===');
console.log('[Blur] Element backdrop-filter:', elComputed.backdropFilter);
console.log('[Blur] Element background:', elComputed.backgroundColor);

// Walk up the DOM tree and log ALL relevant properties
let ancestor = el.parentElement;
let depth = 0;
while (ancestor && ancestor !== document.documentElement) {
const style = ancestor.style;
const computed = getComputedStyle(ancestor);
const tag = ancestor.tagName.toLowerCase();
const id = ancestor.id ? '#' + ancestor.id : '';
const cls = ancestor.className ? '.' + ancestor.className.split(' ')[0] : '';
const label = tag + id + cls;

// Log all potentially problematic properties
const props = {
contain: computed.contain,
filter: computed.filter,
transform: computed.transform,
willChange: computed.willChange,
isolation: computed.isolation,
mixBlendMode: computed.mixBlendMode,
backdropFilter: computed.backdropFilter,
overflow: computed.overflow,
opacity: computed.opacity,
clipPath: computed.clipPath,
background: computed.backgroundColor
};

console.log('[Blur]', depth + ':', label, JSON.stringify(props));

// Fix known problematic properties
if (computed.contain !== 'none') {
style.contain = 'none';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED contain on', label);
}
if (computed.filter !== 'none') {
style.filter = 'none';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED filter on', label);
}
if (computed.transform !== 'none') {
style.transform = 'none';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED transform on', label);
}
if (computed.willChange !== 'auto') {
style.willChange = 'auto';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED will-change on', label);
}
if (computed.isolation === 'isolate') {
style.isolation = 'auto';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED isolation on', label);
}
if (computed.mixBlendMode !== 'normal') {
style.mixBlendMode = 'normal';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED mix-blend-mode on', label);
}

// overflow: hidden can clip backdrop-filter rendering
if (computed.overflow.includes('hidden')) {
style.overflow = 'visible';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED overflow:hidden on', label);
}

// Nested backdrop-filter breaks child backdrop-filter
if (computed.backdropFilter !== 'none') {
style.backdropFilter = 'none';
style.webkitBackdropFilter = 'none';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED backdrop-filter on', label);
}

// Check for semi-opaque backgrounds (blocks blur from seeing through)
const bg = computed.backgroundColor;
if (bg && bg !== 'transparent' && bg !== 'rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)') {
const match = bg.match(/rgba?\((\d+),\s*(\d+),\s*(\d+)(?:,\s*([\d.]+))?\)/);
if (match) {
const alpha = match[4] !== undefined ? parseFloat(match[4]) : 1;
if (alpha > 0.5) {
style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';
console.log('[Blur] ^^^ CLEARED semi-opaque background (' + alpha.toFixed(2) + ') on', label);
}
}
}

ancestor = ancestor.parentElement;
depth++;
}
console.log('[Blur] === Done, checked', depth, 'ancestors ===');
});
})();
</script>

</body>

</html>
